 After about an hour of wandering around searching for the elementals, I was about to kill another cinder goblin shaman when BOOM I stepped forward and right into a pit trap where 4 blazing elementals attempted to gangbang my Erudian ass back to my bind point in the Nexus. Lucky me my water pet was DS'ed and hurried down to my rescue. Out of the four kills, two bloodstones and a Power of Fire dropped! I shouted out my find, screamed my glee to my guild (who had to put up with it because I'm the leader) and did my emoted-happy dance. My guildie dropped down beside me and waited. And waited. Killed 2 spawns. And waited. I had to log for the night while he was still camping the basement spawns on a 25-minute spawn timer so I'm unsure if he got his power yet. I hope he did, it sounds pretty rare:(

